Package eu.fbk.rdfpro.jsonld Description

Parser and writer for RDF in JSON-LD format (depends on Semargl lib).

Parsing depends on the Semargl JSONLD parser, while writing is implemented directly by this factory and can be configured via setting #ROOT_TYPES, which specifies the types of RDF resources to be emitted as top level JSONLD nodes.
